  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurant &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>La Buona Novella </strong>is open for lunch and dinner and uses local seasonal ingredients to create classic Florentine dishes with a contemporary twist. In the summer months (June to October) the restaurant extends into the terrace on the Piazza di Santa Maria Novella.</p>
<p><strong>Three Sixty Rooftop Pool Bar</strong> opens during the summer and serves drinks and snacks by the pool.</p>
<p><br /><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Small Rooftop Pool (Open April to October 7:00am- 9:00pm)</li>
<li>Breakfast Room</li>
<li>Free wifi</li>
<li>Gym (free of charge)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
