  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Premium Rooms</strong> measure 22-26m² and are available with twin or double beds (single rooms and triple rooms are also available). Finished in a contemporary style, they have views over the Santa Maria Novella Cloisters, hotel garden or inner courtyard. Facilities include air conditioning, free wifi, tea and coffee making facilities, complimentary bottled water refreshed daily, minibar, TV, safe, bathrobes, slippers, hairdryer, bathroom with bathtub or walk-in shower.</p>
<p>Other rooms may be available on request. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
